Scenario: A customer would like to have a short slideshow to include onto their Winter festival website. 
          He requests to have only three images inside the slideshow. 
          This will be displayed as an automatic slideshow until a user clicks on the image. 
          
          Create a slideshow that:
          
          -Uses HTML, CSS and JavaScript
           --divs
           --imgs
           --style classes
           --width
           --variables
           --functions
           --conditionals(if statements)
           --for loop and etc. to make this slideshow interactive
           
           *Hint: You may use resources such as SoloLearn, W3Schools and etc. to create this slideshow. 
           
           Enjoy!
           
       
